data.description: Imagine luxury living at an amazing value. Welcome to 1150 Collier Road NW, Unit# H6, a stylish and contemporary residence nestled in the heart of Atlanta's vibrant Collier Green community. FHA approved Collier Green offers a sense of community with well-maintained green spaces and a gated community for added security and privacy. This thoughtfully designed condo offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and modern living. Close to shopping centers and retail hubs for all your needs including diverse dining options showcasing the culinary delights of Atlanta. All close enough to get those daily steps in. It doesn’t end there, right up the street you can perfect that golf swing at the popular Top Golf driving range.  Oh, you don’t feel like leaving your gated community, head over to the renovated pool, remodeled fitness center or play some volleyball with your neighbors.  This one bedroom one bath condo epitomizes the epitome of convenient living without the hefty price tag. When you step inside this move in ready condo, you have wood flooring and newer carpets, which were professionally cleaned giving you a blank canvas to create your personalized living space. Here are some of the highlights of this gem:   • Spacious and well-lit interiors with an open floor plan.  • Modern kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances and ample cabinet space.  • Cozy living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing after a long day.  • Bedrooms with generous closet space for all your storage needs.  • Well-appointed bathrooms with contemporary fixtures.  • Private balcony, ideal for enjoying your morning coffee or evening breeze.  • Just serviced the HVAC  • Re-tiled the shower, upgraded bathroom fixtures  • Upgraded the water heater.     The exterior of the building was painted in the last 3 years and the pool has been renovated.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this modern condo your new home! Contact us to schedule a private viewing and experience the charm of 1150 Collier Road NW, Unit#H6.
